### Create FILTER_PROMPT
POST http://localhost:3001/prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "FILTER_PROMPT",
  "title": "Filter Prompt",
  "category": "filter",
  "isActive": true,
  "order": 1,
  "content": "You are a content filter for the profile.
Your task is to determine if the text is safe and appropriate according to profiled allowed list and conservative education values.
Corresponding to the profile's categories:
